**`views/about.ejs` (About Page)**

```ejs
<%- include('includes/header') %>

<section class="page-content">
    <h2 class="section-title">About Shakiso Poly-Technic College</h2>
    <p>Shakiso Poly-Technic College is a distinguished governmental institution dedicated to providing high-quality technical and vocational education. Located in the vibrant Shakiso City Administration, our college plays a crucial role in empowering the youth with practical skills and knowledge essential for national development.</p>
    <p>Established with a vision to bridge the gap between academic learning and industry demands, we offer a diverse range of programs designed to equip students with the competencies needed to thrive in various sectors. Our curriculum is developed in close collaboration with industry experts to ensure its relevance and effectiveness.</p>
    <h3>Our Vision</h3>
    <p>To be a leading center of excellence in technical and vocational education, fostering innovation, entrepreneurship, and sustainable development in Ethiopia and beyond.</p>
    <h3>Our Mission</h3>
    <p>To provide accessible, quality-driven, and industry-relevant technical and vocational training that empowers students to achieve their full potential, contribute to the economy, and lead fulfilling lives.</p>
    <h3>Core Values</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>**Excellence:** Striving for the highest standards in education and training.</li>
        <li>**Innovation:** Embracing new ideas and technologies to enhance learning.</li>
        <li>**Integrity:** Upholding honesty, ethics, and transparency in all our operations.</li>
        <li>**Community Engagement:** Actively participating in community development initiatives.</li>
        <li>**Student Success:** Committing to the holistic development and career success of our students.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Our state-of-the-art facilities, experienced faculty, and strong industry linkages ensure that our graduates are well-prepared to meet the challenges of the modern workforce. We are proud to contribute to the economic growth and social progress of our region.</p>
</section>

<%- include('includes/footer') %>
```

